{"tid":1900251,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［新聞整理］2019-2020 教育界道德要求","createTime":"2020-02-27T06:19:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-27T12:02:48.000Z","uid":20442,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f028219091e4d3f4025cfae731d9a084080120b9","tid":1900251,"uid":20442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T06:19:17.000Z","msg":"1.香港華人基督教聯會真道書院助理校長戴健暉<br />\n行為：<br />\nFB 仇警<br />\n下場： <br />\n公開致歉，校方事後將其調職，並成立專責委員會跟進及呈交調查報告予教育局<br />\n教育局：<br />\n發譴責信考慮除牌<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2.嘉諾撒聖心書院執教通識科的賴得鐘老師<br />\n行為：<br />\nFB 仇警言論<br />\n下場：<br />\n將涉事圖片刪除並道歉，亦辭任考評局通識教育科科目委員會主席及成員職務<br />\n教育局：<br />\n發譴責信考慮除牌<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/amp/news/realtime/hk/1594516\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Famp%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1594516&d=gsiGAs%2Boihw6EKwg2XwNgQNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=e2e5af45\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Famp%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1594516&h=997cdd0b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/amp/news/realtime/hk/1594516</a><br />\n<br />\n3.銅鑼灣直資學校孔聖堂中學署理副校長何栢欣<br />\n行為：<br />\nFB發表針對警方的「藏頭」詩<br />\n下場：<br />\n校方成立專責調查小組，並把何栢欣暫時停職<br />\n教育局：<br />\n未回應<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=381784\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D381784&d=gsiGAs%2Boihw6EKwg2XwNgQNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=b1fb63eb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D381784&h=aea51437\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=381784</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4.北角閩喬中學副校長宋燕玲<br />\n行為：<br />\nFB 「不歡迎曱甴做學生」<br />\n下場：<br />\n校長羅惠金回覆本報查詢時稱，得知網上流傳有關帖文截圖，她即時向宋副校長查證，確定宋副校長沒有發出有關帖文，「明顯地她facebook帳戶被人入侵，因此要立即停用」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190829/s00001/1567081744488/%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E7%B6%B2%E5%82%B3%E9%96%A9%E5%83%91%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%B8%E5%89%AF%E6%A0%A1fb%E8%B2%BC%E3%80%8C%E6%8B%92%E6%9B%B1%E7%94%B4%E8%AB%96%E3%80%8D-%E6%A0%A1%E6%96%B9-%E5%A5%B9%E5%B8%B3%E6%88%B6%E8%A2%AB%E5%85%A5%E4%BE%B5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190829%2Fs00001%2F1567081744488%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B%25E3%2580%2591%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E5%2582%25B3%25E9%2596%25A9%25E5%2583%2591%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E5%2589%25AF%25E6%25A0%25A1fb%25E8%25B2%25BC%25E3%2580%258C%25E6%258B%2592%25E6%259B%25B1%25E7%2594%25B4%25E8%25AB%2596%25E3%2580%258D-%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E6%2596%25B9-%25E5%25A5%25B9%25E5%25B8%25B3%25E6%2588%25B6%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2585%25A5%25E4%25BE%25B5&d=gsiGAs%2Boihw6EKwg2XwNgQNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=6169aeaa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190829%2Fs00001%2F1567081744488%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B%25E3%2580%2591%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E5%2582%25B3%25E9%2596%25A9%25E5%2583%2591%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E5%2589%25AF%25E6%25A0%25A1fb%25E8%25B2%25BC%25E3%2580%258C%25E6%258B%2592%25E6%259B%25B1%25E7%2594%25B4%25E8%25AB%2596%25E3%2580%258D-%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E6%2596%25B9-%25E5%25A5%25B9%25E5%25B8%25B3%25E6%2588%25B6%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2585%25A5%25E4%25BE%25B5&h=7f786bf3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190829/s00001/1567081744488/%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E7%B6%B2%E5%82%B3%E9%96%A9%E5%83%91%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%B8%E5%89%AF%E6%A0%A1fb%E8%B2%BC%E3%80%8C%E6%8B%92%E6%9B%B1%E7%94%B4%E8%AB%96%E3%80%8D-%E6%A0%A1%E6%96%B9-%E5%A5%B9%E5%B8%B3%E6%88%B6%E8%A2%AB%E5%85%A5%E4%BE%B5</a><br />\n<br />\n5.元朗天主教中學副校長陳秀芬<br />\n行為：<br />\n破壞連儂牆，並說岀「你係咪要X呀？除褲啦！」 等粗言指罵途經的青年<br />\n下場：<br />\n該校稱，尊重每個人有表達意見的權利。校方另向家長發特別通告，表示已就事件啟動危機處理機制<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190906/s00001/1567766832289/%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E5%A4%A9%E4%B8%BB%E6%95%99%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%B8%E5%89%AF%E6%A0%A1%E9%95%B7%E6%B6%89%E7%88%86%E7%B2%97%E6%92%95%E6%96%87%E5%AE%A3-%E6%A0%A1%E6%96%B9%E7%99%BC%E8%81%B2%E6%98%8E-%E5%9A%B4%E5%8E%B2%E8%99%95%E7%90%86\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190906%2Fs00001%2F1567766832289%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%2595%2599%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E5%2589%25AF%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E9%2595%25B7%25E6%25B6%2589%25E7%2588%2586%25E7%25B2%2597%25E6%2592%2595%25E6%2596%2587%25E5%25AE%25A3-%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E6%2596%25B9%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%2581%25B2%25E6%2598%258E-%25E5%259A%25B4%25E5%258E%25B2%25E8%2599%2595%25E7%2590%2586&d=gsiGAs%2Boihw6EKwg2XwNgQNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=3699352e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190906%2Fs00001%2F1567766832289%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%2595%2599%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E5%2589%25AF%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E9%2595%25B7%25E6%25B6%2589%25E7%2588%2586%25E7%25B2%2597%25E6%2592%2595%25E6%2596%2587%25E5%25AE%25A3-%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E6%2596%25B9%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%2581%25B2%25E6%2598%258E-%25E5%259A%25B4%25E5%258E%25B2%25E8%2599%2595%25E7%2590%2586&h=90e47105\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190906/s00001/1567766832289/%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E5%A4%A9%E4%B8%BB%E6%95%99%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%B8%E5%89%AF%E6%A0%A1%E9%95%B7%E6%B6%89%E7%88%86%E7%B2%97%E6%92%95%E6%96%87%E5%AE%A3-%E6%A0%A1%E6%96%B9%E7%99%BC%E8%81%B2%E6%98%8E-%E5%9A%B4%E5%8E%B2%E8%99%95%E7%90%86</a><br />\n<br />\n6.其他老師被抗議、被投手、發表曱甴論，歡迎大家補充<br />\n格式如下：<br />\n［學校全名］［職級人名］<br />\n［行為］<br />\n［下場］<br />\n［如有連結］<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1.整理教育界新聞，以便全港學生跟進校內教師言行<br />\n<br />\n2. 希望全香港對教育界嘅社會期望，推廣到所有政府「父母官」、議員、執法機構、司法機構上，為香港所有未成年人士劃下統一標準<br />\n<br />\n3. 希望各界別領袖都有以身作則，冇出言不遜</span></span><br />\n<br />\n後記：<br />\n細個嗰陣，讀中史唔明白，點解：「清風不識字，何以亂翻書」會被清雍正斬首。<br />\n<br />\n後來，又唔明中國1959 年「反右運動」係乜嚟，點解毛澤東話邊個係「右派」，邊個就要批鬥？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"282f8378a4331355ff162e2bfdf36075af16e711","tid":1900251,"uid":20442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T06:21:29.000Z","msg":"推十連"},{"pid":"75b04ddce33982e878acfc04f53094d113eb48e3","tid":1900251,"uid":20442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T06:21:41.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"c9213364c40481bf05846569860680b23a85fb03","tid":1900251,"uid":20442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T06:21:53.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"270bfc825aa6bb6a66438c128ab01beb95bd4143","tid":1900251,"uid":286897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T06:23:02.000Z","msg":"3月考評局就會公佈dse考場如果種到上述呢間學校嘅話歡迎做紅衛兵 參觀下間學校啲personal office<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fa